2019-12-18 12:56:12	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> required properties would be not nilable without a default, so they would fail when trying to parse the config
2019-12-18 12:59:02	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> plan would also be to have some pre processing step to replace placeholders with ENV vars/parameters
2019-12-18 12:59:55	FromGitter	<tenebrousedge> okay
